nts for the home our products in the furniture products category include adjustable bed bases ornamental headboards and footboards bed frames bedding accessories seat recliner mechanisms and controls sleepers lifts seating components furniture bases curved plywood and components for office furniture manufacturers jay thompson – president adjustable bed group go to furniture products leggett  platts diverse array of specialized products includes automotive seating support structures and comfort systems a category in which were the worlds foremost designer and manufacturer steel tubing for the aerospace industry and finally commercial vehicle products dan culbertson – division controller go to specialized products     customer payment portal po terms  conditions supplier information environmental stewardship site map government compliance information corporate governance proxy statement annual report equal opportunity policy human trafficking policypdf conflict minerals policy security notice scam illegally references leggett  platt copyright   leggett  platt inc all rights reserved terms of use link policy privacy policy privacy shield policy for problems with this site – contact internet solutions specialized products site map annual report k proxy statement corporate governance supplier documents home business segments residential products industrial products furniture products specialized products our company news investor relations careers contacts specialized products leggett  platts specialized products can be found in numerous markets in the automotive industry were the worlds foremost designer and manufacturer of seating support and comfort systems we are also a major supplier of titanium nickel and stainless steel tubing for the aerospace industry finally we manufacture and install a variety of products for commercial vehicle use automotive lp automotive group aerospace lp aerospace commercial vehicle products masterack click for a complete list of all legge