t  platt machinery group continues to grow in capabilities and physical locations lpmg now operates nearly a dozen plants around the world north america carthage missouri is the location for the international headquarters of leggett  platt lpmg is based here within the lp machine products division offices this branch handles key management and engineering services for lpmg nearly all interaction with us companies is coordinated through this branch our other lpmg north american manufacturing locations are focused in specialized machinery and parts cycloindex vertex fasteners global systems group europe our croatian company lpt leggett  platt technologies is another advantageous location creative engineers combine both metal fabrication and plastic molding techniques to produce unique solutions for our customers lp has related facilities in germany russia france uk and other european nations asia lpmg has a growing facility in shanghai china a large staff of machinists automated production and sourcing specialists results in quality manufacturing resources cnc machines and rapid tooling machines produce a high volume of machined products and specialized machines other branches of lp also have manufacturing facilities in various provinces of china as well as several sales and service offices throughout most asian regions your browser is outofdate update your browser to view this website correctly update my browser now × leggett  platt® commercial vehicle products contact us leggett  platt cvp � headquarters  mellon court decatur ga   email leggett  platt cvp leggett  platt commercial vehicle products wherever the job takes you be ready with ourdurable upfit options leggett  platt cvp is unique in the industry because we offer our clients a wide breadth of products and services in one simple package serving the fleet market since  our longstanding industry experience translates to success for our customers contact us today and find out why our fleet and leasing customer